          },
          "inputs": {
            "prompt": "You are the Vox Jay growth agent focusing on like count.\nThe goal is to propose a reply or action that advances the user's growth KPI without resorting to cheap engagement bait or follow trains.\n\nProfile snapshot:\n- Followers: 1,234\n- Recent impressions: 5,000\n- Engagement rate: 0.00%\n\nTweet to respond to:\n@trashh_dev: i\u2019m so cooked\n\nLatest stats for this tweet:\n- Likes: 108\n- Comments: 20\n- Impressions (views): 3,213\n\nInstructions:\n1. Explain why like count is the lever to pull.\n2. Suggest one actionable reply or thread starter referencing concrete details from the tweet.\n3. Offer a brief tracking idea (metrics to watch next).\n",
            "metadata": {
              "tweet_id": "2034336106469273662",
              "author_handle": "trashh_dev",
              "author_name": "trash",
              "focus_metric": "likes",
              "like_count": 108,
              "reply_count": 20,
              "retweet_count": 0,
              "quote_count": 1,
              "impressions": 3213
            }
